articles.author: Lim Hui Jie
articles.title: Asia markets mixed as U.S. debt ceiling talks end with no deal - CNBC
articles.description: Asian markets trade higher as talk between U.S. President Joe Biden and congressional leaders on the debt ceiling ends with no deal so far.
articles.content:
Asia-Pacific markets were mixed on Tuesday as talks between U.S President Joe Biden and House Speaker Kevin McCarthy ended without a deal.
